Chinese.name: COS日志文件简易分析
Chinese.description: 本函数将源 bucket 中的 COS 日志文件进行简易分析，处理后将结果上传到指定 bucket
Chinese.attention: 该函数模板仅供 COS 控制台使用，请勿自行创建

English.name: AnalyzeLogs
English.description: This function will download cos log files from source bucket, analyze them, and upload result file to target bucket
English.attention: This function template is only provided to COS console, please do not use it by yourself
